    <p>UNEP is a strategic partner with AGEDI and EAD as outlined in Section 1.4. The following UNEP sections will work in partnership with EAD and AGEDI during the West Asia SOER-Live project: </p>
    <ul>
      <li>The Division of Early Warning and Assessment (DEWA-Africa) aims to improve access to meaningful environmental data and information, and increase capacity to use environmental information for decision-making and action.</li>
      <li>The Regional Office for West Asia (ROWA) coordinates UNEP's programme of work in the region. The Regional Office acts as the link between UNEP and the countries in the region, and promotes collaboration and partnerships with organisations active in sustainable development in West Asia. </li>
    </ul>
